{"tid":185326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英大學假證書網上有售！民建聯多人學歷受質疑","createTime":"2017-04-03T11:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T12:10:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e35229ed4c3f4f196ad8541f46a87dc6bd63587","tid":185326,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>英大學假證書網上有售！民建聯多人學歷受質疑<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170402/56510929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170402%2F56510929&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d6082fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170402%2F56510929&h=c6d3b373\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170402/56510929</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170401/large/1491051223_9398.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170401%2Flarge%2F1491051223_9398.png&h=95868913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名民建聯成員的學歷備受質疑，有議員聲稱持博士學位，但相關大學根本未獲政府認可，又有成員捲入國力書院醜聞。至於柯創盛報稱讀過的英國諾丁漢特倫特大學（Nottingham Trent University，NTU），則是獲國際認可的院校，但記者發現不少外國網站均有出售該校的假證書。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯過往多次捲入學歷爭議，該黨立法會議員葛珮帆2012年選舉時報稱擁有「Greenwich University, Hawaii」的博士學位，但後來遭獨立股評人David Webb踢爆該校與英國名校Greenwich University（格林威治大學）毫無關係，「校址」更只是校長的住址，非但從未獲當地教育部門認可，最後更倒閉收場。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯區議員鄭琴淵則透過國力書院入讀一間菲律賓大學，以不足一年時間「極速」博士畢業。黨友鍾樹根自稱擁有英國威爾斯大學碩士學位，但2011年被BBC踢爆該校向海外連繫學校濫發學位，證書價值令人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n柯創盛接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，自己當年入讀港大持續進修學院（SPACE）與暨南大學合辦的課程，取得社會科學學士學位，但他拒絕出示畢業證書。記者翻查資料，卻未能找到相關的學士課程，反而找到鍾樹根曾入讀SPACE與暨大合辦的社會科學文憑課程資料，未知柯是否混淆了文憑與學士兩種資歷。<br />\n<br />\n至於NTU雖然獲英國官方認可，但根據QS排行榜，其世界排名不入首700名，國內排名亦只有64。記者又發現，多個外國網站都有出售NTU的虛假畢業證書，其中「<a href=\"http://documentscenter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocumentscenter.com&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=1f5d0a09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">documentscenter.com</a>」每張證書索價約6,200港元，課程紀錄則盛惠約4,000港元。"},{"pid":"fa1342130e17d42027cb2704362b976a3a87c117","tid":185326,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"精彩重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ICz5lDA290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ICz5lDA290&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=2ffa0068\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ICz5lDA290</a>"},{"pid":"67947f73386af8ef99ec53d7b747b3e4eca8fdb5","tid":185326,"uid":52687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"讀Diploma 扮degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d124d612fa570c334e3671e106cbd7ad1e59174","tid":185326,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cddd6b8348b73e2b180885a6950d7f167e5d8de","tid":185326,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"諾定咸就諾定咸啦，乜撚諾丁漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41a63646823e9068a01bbeb1d06470558be70f0","tid":185326,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諾定咸就諾定咸啦，乜撚諾丁漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貝漢克姆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51da2bbc2c69811b04be98acbb7ad6142304641f","tid":185326,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl